  <title>Ein aufgenommenes Foto oder Video betrachten</title>

  <p>After you take a photo or record a video, it will appear in the photo
  stream at the bottom of the window. You can right-click it and press
  <gui style="menuitem">Open</gui> to open it in the photo viewer or video
  player application.</p>

